{"tid":365671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際聯著：三人媲美緬甸昂山素姬","createTime":"2017-08-19T12:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T15:33:51.000Z","uid":58099,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df8aab6395f3b4b6802f5c0f6cd959ecac7b2289","tid":365671,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"國際聯箸讚揚三子的行動開創了香港大型的政治抗爭運動，守護香港的自由，抗衡野心日增的北京。<br />\n<br />\n文章把三人媲美國際知名的人權鬥士如俄羅斯薩哈羅夫、捷克哈維爾及緬甸昂山素姬，因為這等人士均因非法集會罪名而被定罪懲處，並認為三子連同近年其他香港年青人的抗爭，其意義遠超越於對他們自身或香港前途的影響，亦是與其他著名領袖並肩，促使一個獨裁的中國政府兌現其國際及政治承諾。"},{"pid":"8525de983fd5d473c4b377515af820d27b56792b","tid":365671,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ecc653df2ced4b1762f48445f4ed632039771c2","tid":365671,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:21:01.000Z","msg":"是味有點兒哪個個"},{"pid":"b72e0e23a89f9574f331cc29fb0154ac4469f4f1","tid":365671,"uid":99973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a469520d3e8080aa14a7efc69359db2b3fb6a8","tid":365671,"uid":4060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"國際聯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>箸</del>署</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd475f8ab1eaab66d33942cf2b9112e796c66c6","tid":365671,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f45e57e6e0c46fa562bc0b22878225f73c9ad4e3","tid":365671,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2dbf1c7a5fd67a5b169b409c2bdf1d3f979f75b","tid":365671,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"749